name: A. Flea
description: The tiniest and most athletic of all Looney Tunes characters, A. Flea is a street-wise red-brown flea who usually takes part in antics involving muscular weightlifters. Despite his tiny size he often gets the better of larger opponents.

name: Actor Sean Astin
description: Sean Astin is an American actor, director and producer, best known for playing Samwise Gamgee in The Lord of the Rings trilogy and Mikey Walsh in The Goonies.
